|           |-- app
|               |-- NetworkManagementApp.java
|-- pom.xml

--- Topology ---

Network Topology:

[ SNMP-Enabled Device (192.168.1.1) ]
          |
          |-- SNMPClient

[ NETCONF-Enabled Router (192.168.1.2) ]
          |
          |-- NETCONFClient

[ RESTCONF Server (192.168.1.3) ]
          |
          |-- RESTCONFClient

[ Prometheus PushGateway (localhost:9091) ]
          |
          |-- TelemetryCollector

--- Code Implementation ---
